お客様より、EIN番号など情報は伝えたが、さらにDHLから、製造施設名と住所を伝えてほしいと連絡があり、対応してほしいと連絡がありました。
こちらペガサスにご連絡いただくことはできますでしょうか？
▼（先方より）
Dear Mr. Koshiro Matsui,
I sent in my EIN + SS4 information to DHL. Later, I got another message from DHL saying more information is missing :(
This is the link from DHL - <https://sdus.dhl.com/awb-profile?awbNumber=9154287704> . It looks like they want the HTS code and the full name and address of the facility where this was manufactured. Please provide them this information when you get a chance.
It looks like somehow the customs related information was dropped in the first shipping request? Or maybe some miscommunication? I'd greatly appreciate it if you could take a deeper look at this shipment so it clears customs quickly. In my experience once it gets "stuck" in customs it just becomes much harder to clear ... so I very much want to avoid getting stuck :)

Thanks,
Krishnan

P.S.
I'm sending this information via email and Alibaba.
